# basePath RS-4Y

:: emergeFromTheIce
@trigger    PlayerEnterRegion
@when       regionId == "CurrentExit", !HasUpgrade("Engine"), scene:lastEntrance == "RS-4X"
@triggerPriority   High
@once
@cutscene
{@player}   What| just happened!?
{@kevin}    It seems like our ship's {h}engine{/h} isn't strong enough to resist the pull of the current!
            Perhaps we should go consult {nameof @merchant} to upgrade our ship if we're going to continue exploring here.